name: Julie Kendall
introduction: Julie Kendall is an actress, spokesperson and lifestyle model based in Atlanta, GA. She started acting 12 years ago, when she enrolled in an acting class that was intended to help her overcome a huge fear of public speaking; something that was required of her to do, often, for her profession as a Sales Manager. Through her acting classes, she quickly discovered her true passion in life, tapped into her courage and determination and left her then lucrative job, to pursue her dreams. In a short time she has made a name for herself with lead and supporting roles in several award winning films and TV series.
